ficial Insemination</em>";s:18:"UF_ADM_POSITION_EN";s:16:"General Director";s:19:"~UF_ADM_POSITION_EN";s:16:"General Director";s:12:"UF_DEGREE_EN";s:5:"DSc. ";s:13:"~UF_DEGREE_EN";s:5:"DSc. ";s:17:"UF_NAME_DATIVE_EN";N;s:18:"~UF_NAME_DATIVE_EN";N;s:16:"UF_PAGE_TITLE_EN";s:31:"#FULL_NAME# — #SEO_SPECIALTY#";s:17:"~UF_PAGE_TITLE_EN";s:31:"#FULL_NAME# — #SEO_SPECIALTY#";s:16:"UF_PAGE_DESCR_EN";s:15:"#WORK_POSITION#";s:17:"~UF_PAGE_DESCR_EN";s:15:"#WORK_POSITION#";s:19:"UF_PAGE_KEYWORDS_EN";N;s:20:"~UF_PAGE_KEYWORDS_EN";N;s:17:"UF_DESCRIPTION_EN";s:1881:"&lt;p&gt;
	 Work experience in the speciality -&nbsp;#FROM_1970#. Teaching experience at the Chair of Obstetrics and Gynecology of the Pavlov Saint-Petersburg State Medical University - 35 years.
